1
00:00:08,220 --> 00:00:10,940
♪Hush now, don't disturb
the moonlight on the pond♪

2
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,900
♪A shattered heart
rests pillowed in my chest♪

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:17,580
♪I would shield you♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,580
♪From this cruel wind and frost♪

5
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:25,460
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

6
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:29,260
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

7
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:31,580
♪This lingering afterglow♪

8
00:00:31,580 --> 00:00:35,420
♪Holds the image
of our very first glance♪

9
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:40,100
♪I borrow a thousand-year wind
to caress your gauze window♪

10
00:00:40,460 --> 00:00:44,420
♪Tailoring moonlight
into your luminous gown♪

11
00:00:44,900 --> 00:00:50,820
♪Severing the past,
weaving a thousand yards of splendor♪

12
00:00:51,380 --> 00:00:54,980
♪With a thousand-year dream,
I seek the fragrance of your hair♪

13
00:00:55,220 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Pouring a lifetime of passion
into the silk you wear♪

14
00:00:59,660 --> 00:01:05,660
♪In this splendid world,
wherever you are is paradise♪

15
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:12,460
=The Silk Master from the Future=

16
00:01:12,580 --> 00:01:17,460
=Episode 11=

17
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,360
Well,

18
00:01:19,360 --> 00:01:20,520
who'd have known?

19
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,960
You're now

20
00:01:21,960 --> 00:01:23,520
a famous figure in Feng City.

21
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:25,440
Come on. I'm just getting started.

22
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:27,160
Haven't you heard that saying?

23
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:29,720
Fear not the road ahead
for lack of a friend,

24
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:32,120
for who in this wide world
does not know you?

25
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:34,520
Fear not the road ahead
for lack of a friend,

26
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,240
for who in this wide world
does not know you?

27
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:39,640
What a great poem. Who composed it?

28
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:41,200
Well,

29
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,240
I composed it, of course.

30
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,560
You can compose poems?

31
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,360
You'll find out that

32
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:47,760
your husband

33
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,200
has many talents.

34
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:51,600
(My husband?)

35
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,320
(But who do you truly love?)

36
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:55,560
(The Zhou family's hired hand)

37
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:57,360
(who stood up for you,)

38
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,960
(or your wife, Zhou Xingyu?)

39
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,800
The heir of Marquis House,

40
00:02:03,800 --> 00:02:05,480
Mr. Lu, has arrived.

41
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:07,720
Why is he everywhere?

42
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,360
This is just
an ordinary poetry gathering.

43
00:02:10,120 --> 00:02:11,000
What's he

44
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:11,800
doing here?

45
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:13,560
He's probably here for the fun too.

46
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:15,800
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
My lord.

47
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,280
Mm.

48
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:17,360
Welcome.

49
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,680
Your seat has already been prepared.

50
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:27,720
Mr. Chen.

51
00:02:30,760 --> 00:02:32,160
Do you know why this poetry gathering

52
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:34,480
could attract the heir of Marquis House,

53
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:37,120
and even the newly appointed
top scholar, Chen Hongyun?

54
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,800
Isn't it because the winner

55
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,000
of the poetry gathering

56
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:41,480
gets to sleep with the top courtesan

57
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:42,480
from the capital?

58
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,360
This top courtesan is none other than

59
00:02:44,680 --> 00:02:46,760
Chancellor Sun's granddaughter,

60
00:02:46,760 --> 00:02:48,240
Xue Bingxiu.

61
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:49,800
Xue Bingxiu?

62
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:52,560
Why did she come to Chunfeng Pavilion
as a courtesan?

63
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:53,280
She had no choice

64
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,520
but to hide her identity this way.

65
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,360
The Shadow Guards

66
00:02:57,320 --> 00:02:58,240
found out that

67
00:02:58,240 --> 00:02:59,640
she has the late emperor's

68
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:02,120
posthumous edict,
left by Chancellor Sun.

69
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,400
What?

70
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:04,600
The late emperor's posthumous edict?

71
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:07,360
But haven't you already
taken the throne?

72
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:08,880
How could Chancellor Sun

73
00:03:08,880 --> 00:03:10,200
have the late emperor's edict?

74
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:12,480
The Shadow Guards
are still investigating this.

75
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,680
But ever since I ascended the throne,

76
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:17,200
the officials in court
led by Prince Ning

77
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,880
have had plenty of complaints.

78
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:21,600
In recent years,
they've grown even more restless.

79
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,760
Chancellor Sun was assassinated

80
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,800
because of the late emperor's edict.

81
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:28,120
So this edict must never

82
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,720
fall into Prince Ning's hands.

83
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:32,000
So,

84
00:03:32,160 --> 00:03:34,120
Lu Qifeng and the others

85
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,880
are after the late emperor's edict

86
00:03:35,880 --> 00:03:37,000
in Xue Bingxiu's hands.

87
00:03:37,800 --> 00:03:38,280
That's right.

88
00:03:38,640 --> 00:03:40,480
To obtain this edict,

89
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,600
one must win the poetry gathering

90
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,920
and get close to her.

91
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:46,520
Li Yunhe is full of clever strategies,

92
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,320
but poetry is different from couplets.

93
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,120
I'm afraid

94
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:54,600
he won't be of much use

95
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,760
at this poetry contest.

96
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,600
This one is really good.

97
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,920
- Bravo!
- Good!

98
00:05:36,480 --> 00:05:38,760
- Great!
- Bravo!

99
00:05:52,980 --> 00:05:54,780
♪I awake a thousand years later♪

100
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:57,700
♪In this unfamiliar place♪

101
00:06:00,540 --> 00:06:02,220
♪You wait a thousand miles away♪

102
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:05,820
♪In those mottled, fading days♪

103
00:06:07,980 --> 00:06:11,460
♪See the silk blanket the long hallway♪

104
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:14,820
♪Steamings, boiling,
time turns yellowed and worn♪

105
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:17,300
♪I shift the warp and weft♪

106
00:06:17,300 --> 00:06:21,860
♪Calculating the sharp edges of fate♪

107
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:23,120
(Sun Yanyan,)

108
00:06:23,120 --> 00:06:25,480
(Chancellor Sun's granddaughter.)

109
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:27,360
(After Chancellor Sun's death,
she fled the capital.)

110
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:28,880
(She changed her name)

111
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,360
(to Xue Bingxiu.)

112
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:33,360
♪I would shield you
from this cruel wind and frost♪

113
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:35,200
How can there be such

114
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:37,080
a devastatingly beautiful woman?

115
00:06:37,080 --> 00:06:38,640
Xue Bingxiu, I love you!

116
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:41,240
♪The russet cloth
brushes against my heart♪

117
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:44,620
♪Like sunset
draping over your shoulders♪

118
00:06:44,660 --> 00:06:49,540
♪This lingering afterglow holds
the image of our very first glance♪

119
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,280
Humph!

120
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,520
Yu,

121
00:06:55,280 --> 00:06:55,760
I...

122
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,960
I was just looking.

123
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:57,840
Just looking?

124
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,320
You were staring straight at her.

125
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,840
But I... I paid for this.

126
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,640
What? You!

127
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,720
No, no.

128
00:07:03,720 --> 00:07:05,240
It's not the kind of payment
you're thinking of.

129
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,320
Then what kind of payment is it?

130
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,920
Well, you'll see in a moment.

131
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,760
Everyone, welcome

132
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,240
to this poetry contest

133
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,320
hosted by the Prefect's Office

134
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:19,080
and organized by Chunfeng Pavilion.

135
00:07:19,080 --> 00:07:21,480
And we'd like to thank
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk

136
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,880
for its strong support of this contest.

137
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:29,740
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk.)

138
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:40,440
(Tang Xian Gambiered Silk.)

139
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,280
Well?

140
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:43,040
How do you like

141
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,640
my advertisement?

142
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,440
Advertisement?

143
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:49,760
It means making something widely known.

144
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:50,520
Anyway,

145
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:52,160
it's a new way of promotion.

146
00:07:58,640 --> 00:08:01,160
Gambiered Silk was originally called
Rustling Silk.

147
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:03,560
It is the soft gold of the textile world

148
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:05,440
and a luxury among silks.

149
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:07,040
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk

150
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:07,840
goes through

151
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:10,720
steamings, boilings, and sun-dries,

152
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:12,440
with more than 30 steps

153
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:14,200
of meticulous craftsmanship.

154
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:17,080
It is soft yet well-structured,

155
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,680
lightweight and hard to wrinkle,

156
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,040
durable and long-lasting,

157
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,720
comfortable and breathable.

158
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:25,040
Li Yunhe really is talented.

159
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:26,800
Not only did he change

160
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:28,160
Rustling Silk to Gambiered Silk,

161
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,920
but he also thought of this method

162
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,240
to promote it

163
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,480
at the poetry contest.

164
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,840
That scumbag.

165
00:08:34,360 --> 00:08:36,200
I spent 500 taels

166
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,440
attending the poetry gathering,

167
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:39,880
and he came here to sell
Gambiered Silk for the Zhous.

168
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,680
Wear Tang Xian Gambiered Silk,

169
00:08:41,680 --> 00:08:44,360
and be a happy person.

170
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,920
- Nice!
- Bravo!

171
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,440
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk.

172
00:08:53,680 --> 00:08:54,960
What is the Zhou family trying to do?

173
00:08:55,240 --> 00:08:56,280
After Rustling Silk lost

174
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:58,040
its qualification as a royal tribute,

175
00:08:58,160 --> 00:08:59,240
the Zhou family got anxious.

176
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:01,280
They want to rebrand themselves
and start over.

177
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:04,480
But this strange method does seem like

178
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:06,560
the work of the Zhou family's
live-in son-in-law,

179
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:08,040
Li Yunhe.

180
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:10,840
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
Li Yunhe? He's here too?

181
00:09:11,840 --> 00:09:13,040
He's sitting over there.

182
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:15,360
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)

183
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,400
Li Yunhe,

184
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,840
I was just wondering
how to deal with you,

185
00:09:20,400 --> 00:09:22,280
and you came right to me.

186
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,160
The theme

187
00:09:24,160 --> 00:09:26,040
of this poetry contest.

188
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,400
(Wine)
The word "wine"

189
00:09:36,400 --> 00:09:37,400
(Wine)
on this scroll.

190
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,800
Wine?

191
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:45,600
(Wine)
Meanwhile,

192
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:47,080
(Wine)
we would also like to thank

193
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,400
(Wine)
Tang Xian Gambiered Silk again

194
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,920
(Wine)
for sponsoring the scroll

195
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:51,280
(Wine)
for this poetry contest.

196
00:09:51,280 --> 00:09:52,000
I must say,

197
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:55,440
Xue Bingxiu is truly
professional at her work.

198
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,760
Mr. Li,

199
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:59,720
Miss Xue said

200
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,600
whoever wins first place today

201
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,160
may enter her chamber

202
00:10:03,160 --> 00:10:04,400
and spend the night with her.

203
00:10:04,800 --> 00:10:05,480
Are you

204
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,480
not tempted?

205
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,560
In your heart,

206
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:09,360
is your husband

207
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:11,000
that kind of person?

208
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,200
I guess so.

209
00:10:12,800 --> 00:10:14,000
But...

210
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,040
But what?

211
00:10:15,400 --> 00:10:16,240
Look.

212
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,080
Should we talk to

213
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,560
Ms. Sun again later?

214
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:20,200
Tonight's bedding

215
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,400
for Miss Xue,

216
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,320
we can sponsor it with our silk too.

217
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,920
What?

218
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:25,720
What do you think?

219
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,000
I think it's a little disgusting.

220
00:10:28,680 --> 00:10:29,480
All right.

221
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:31,800
Now you may freely display

222
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,920
your talents.

223
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:35,200
Wine is the essence of grain.

224
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:37,000
Using wine as the theme

225
00:10:37,040 --> 00:10:38,560
symbolizes Feng City's future

226
00:10:38,560 --> 00:10:39,640
with favorable weather

227
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:40,880
and abundant grain.

228
00:10:40,880 --> 00:10:42,600
Brilliant. Wonderful.

229
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,600
My lord, focus on the bigger picture.

230
00:10:47,560 --> 00:10:48,680
Obtain the late emperor's edict

231
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:50,440
that the chancellor left
with Xue Bingxiu

232
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,640
before dealing with Li Yunhe.

233
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,440
I can't tolerate him for one second!

234
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,040
I'll go first.

235
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:06,080
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)

236
00:11:08,720 --> 00:11:12,480
One petal, two petals, three, and four.

237
00:11:13,640 --> 00:11:17,280
Five petals, six petals,
seven, and eight.

238
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:21,280
If you ask where the red flowers drift,

239
00:11:22,640 --> 00:11:24,520
(Daqian's Poet Laureate)
into her chamber

240
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,240
and vanish without a trace.

241
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:31,240
- Amazing!
- Good poem!

242
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:34,000
- Amazing!
- Good poem!

243
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,080
- Great poem!
- Great poem!

244
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:38,800
- That's amazing!
- Great poem!

245
00:11:39,480 --> 00:11:41,320
One petal, two petals?

246
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:43,400
Even a three-year-old boy

247
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,280
could do that.

248
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,400
This counts as poetry?

249
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,000
I could make a dozen of these.

250
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:52,080
One piece, two pieces, three, and four.

251
00:11:52,640 --> 00:11:55,640
Five pieces, six pieces,
seven, and eight.

252
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,480
If you ask where the pastries went,

253
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,920
into my belly and disappeared.

254
00:12:05,800 --> 00:12:08,400
If you ask where the red flowers drift,

255
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:11,200
into her chamber
and vanish without a trace.

256
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:13,800
A good poem.

257
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,600
It truly is a good poem.

258
00:12:16,520 --> 00:12:18,080
My lord, you truly deserve to be

259
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,440
the future Marquis of Zhennan.

260
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:20,840
Such great talent.

261
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,400
Mr. Chen,

262
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,440
what do you think of the poem
I just made?

263
00:12:25,920 --> 00:12:27,040
My lord, your poetic talent

264
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:28,760
is truly unmatched in the world.

265
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:29,840
That can be called a good poem?

266
00:12:29,920 --> 00:12:31,640
Well, of course.
He's the heir of the Marquis of Zhennan.

267
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:33,200
Even if he took a huge dump,

268
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,360
people would hold it up and say

269
00:12:35,040 --> 00:12:36,400
it smells wonderful.

270
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,800
Keep your voice down.

271
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:42,400
Li Yunhe!

272
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,000
Li Yunhe,

273
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:46,840
I've had enough of you!

274
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:48,240
Get out here!

275
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,120
Wait.

276
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,360
Of all the people in here,

277
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,680
why is he only targeting me?

278
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,120
You humiliated him

279
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,400
so obviously just now.

280
00:12:56,400 --> 00:12:57,520
How could he not target you?

281
00:12:57,520 --> 00:12:59,240
My voice got louder
before I even noticed.

282
00:13:03,640 --> 00:13:04,520
My lord,

283
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,520
what a coincidence.

284
00:13:05,960 --> 00:13:07,480
You came to the poetry contest too?

285
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,520
I can go wherever I want.

286
00:13:10,520 --> 00:13:11,720
It's none of your business!

287
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,680
It was all a misunderstanding.

288
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:14,880
Just now,

289
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:17,320
I was amazed by your talent

290
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,680
and couldn't help but
cry out in admiration.

291
00:13:19,400 --> 00:13:20,920
I didn't mean to startle you.

292
00:13:20,920 --> 00:13:21,600
You know,

293
00:13:21,600 --> 00:13:23,480
my admiration for you

294
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,000
is like an endless roaring river,

295
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:26,320
flowing on and on.

296
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:27,840
I knew a mud-footed peasant like you,

297
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,560
who barely reads a single word,

298
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,920
would know nothing about poetry.

299
00:13:31,920 --> 00:13:32,920
My lord,

300
00:13:32,920 --> 00:13:34,000
you are absolutely right.

301
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:36,080
Everyone in Feng City knows

302
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:36,920
that I am

303
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,480
an illiterate man.

304
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:44,960
(So,)

305
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,920
(the verse
"A man, a plan, a canal, Panama")

306
00:13:47,400 --> 00:13:49,760
(must have been his work.)

307
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:51,840
Mr. Li,

308
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:55,680
I have long heard of your great name.

309
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,000
Now that I've met you,

310
00:13:57,000 --> 00:13:58,200
you truly are handsome

311
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,280
and extraordinary.

312
00:14:00,000 --> 00:14:01,080
May I ask if you would

313
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:03,280
show everyone your talent?

314
00:14:03,880 --> 00:14:04,760
Mr. Li,

315
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:06,960
since Miss Xue has invited you herself,

316
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,680
show us what you can do.

317
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,400
Many talents have gathered today to

318
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,360
make friends through poetry.

319
00:14:11,360 --> 00:14:12,080
Mr. Li,

320
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:14,080
you are also a celebrity in Feng City.

321
00:14:14,080 --> 00:14:15,360
Compose one too.

322
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,480
Thank you, Miss Xue

323
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,960
and everyone, for your kindness.

324
00:14:19,200 --> 00:14:21,200
However, poetry is not

325
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:23,320
my strong suit.

326
00:14:23,720 --> 00:14:24,520
But,

327
00:14:27,200 --> 00:14:28,040
if anyone is interested

328
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:30,080
in our Tang Xian Gambiered Silk,

329
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,400
you may come to me.

330
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:33,000
Our Gambiered Silk...

331
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:35,040
Mr. Li,

332
00:14:35,280 --> 00:14:36,960
this is Chunfeng Pavilion,

333
00:14:36,960 --> 00:14:38,360
not the Zhou family's shop.

334
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:40,280
Please know when to stop.

335
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:41,280
Oh.

336
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:43,760
I'm sorry. My apologies.

337
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,320
Lu Qifeng

338
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,840
has humiliated him to his face,

339
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:51,320
yet he can still stay calm

340
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,760
and promote Gambiered Silk.

341
00:14:53,520 --> 00:14:54,920
He's truly unfazed by honor or disgrace.

342
00:14:55,720 --> 00:14:56,960
He's almost

343
00:14:57,760 --> 00:14:59,800
as shameless as you, Wang.

344
00:15:00,680 --> 00:15:03,280
Yunzhuo, why don't we castrate him

345
00:15:03,640 --> 00:15:04,440
and take him

346
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:06,720
to the palace
to be Mr. Wang's successor?

347
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:08,520
Here you go again.

348
00:15:09,040 --> 00:15:10,120
Your Highness, please stop.

349
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:12,040
Mr. Li is a man of brilliant mind

350
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:14,680
and boundless vision.

351
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:17,240
He is destined to be
the pillar of our nation.

352
00:15:17,640 --> 00:15:19,160
He's so superior.

353
00:15:19,160 --> 00:15:20,520
I'm nothing to him.

354
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:22,000
How boring.

355
00:15:23,160 --> 00:15:25,160
Since this is a contest of poetry,

356
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:26,600
I'll compose one too.

357
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,040
Miss,

358
00:15:28,040 --> 00:15:29,040
you're a woman.

359
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:31,040
Why did you come to Chunfeng Pavilion?

360
00:15:31,680 --> 00:15:32,280
Miss,

361
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:34,320
could it be that you want to beat Mr. Lu

362
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,600
and then have Miss Xue

363
00:15:35,600 --> 00:15:36,840
take you to her chamber?

364
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:37,720
What could two girls

365
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:39,120
possibly do in a chamber?

366
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:44,120
A group of grown men

367
00:15:44,120 --> 00:15:45,960
picking on a young lady?

368
00:15:45,960 --> 00:15:47,240
Do you find it amusing?

369
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,120
Whether a poem is good or not

370
00:15:49,120 --> 00:15:50,120
has nothing to do with

371
00:15:50,120 --> 00:15:51,240
being a man or a woman.

372
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,800
I find this lady

373
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:54,440
quite amazing.

374
00:15:54,440 --> 00:15:55,920
This poetry contest

375
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:58,120
is supposed to be
a gathering of talents and beauties,

376
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,640
where we make friends through literature

377
00:15:59,640 --> 00:16:00,920
and compose poetry and couplets.

378
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,920
Aren't you afraid of being laughed at

379
00:16:02,920 --> 00:16:04,880
for saying something so vulgar?

380
00:16:04,880 --> 00:16:05,680
Miss,

381
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:07,960
don't you know the prize

382
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,720
for today's poetry gathering?

383
00:16:09,720 --> 00:16:10,720
You!

384
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,800
Shame on you!

385
00:16:12,520 --> 00:16:14,560
My sister is playful at her age.

386
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,240
Please don't take offense.

387
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:18,920
Since this is a poetry contest,

388
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,200
I shall also compose a poem.

389
00:16:52,380 --> 00:16:55,980
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

390
00:16:56,140 --> 00:16:59,340
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

391
00:16:59,860 --> 00:17:02,580
♪Who took the March rain♪

392
00:17:02,820 --> 00:17:06,180
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

393
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:09,340
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

394
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:12,700
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

395
00:17:13,580 --> 00:17:19,500
♪Needle and thread
stitch away the marks of time♪

396
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:22,980
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

397
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:26,060
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

398
00:17:26,220 --> 00:17:28,500
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

399
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:32,700
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

400
00:17:32,780 --> 00:17:36,060
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

401
00:17:36,220 --> 00:17:39,340
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

402
00:17:39,860 --> 00:17:42,780
♪In this life I'd be a cloud-tailor♪

403
00:17:42,940 --> 00:17:49,460
♪Never failing the stars,
nor failing you♪

404
00:18:15,740 --> 00:18:19,260
♪Fine rain falls outside the pavilion♪

405
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:22,660
♪With honors won, an old friend returns♪

406
00:18:23,260 --> 00:18:25,980
♪Who took the March rain♪

407
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:29,500
♪To dye the silk against the skin♪

408
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:32,780
♪Yam juice enriches the silk threads♪

409
00:18:32,860 --> 00:18:36,580
♪Weaving the Milky Way
down to the mortal world♪

410
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:39,900
♪Warp and weft entwine,
one shuttle, one dream♪

411
00:18:39,900 --> 00:18:42,860
♪As seasons change♪

412
00:18:42,860 --> 00:18:46,500
♪Cutting a yard of the misty rain♪

413
00:18:46,500 --> 00:18:49,340
♪Embroidering half a scroll
of earthly verses♪

414
00:18:49,420 --> 00:18:51,980
♪Where the golden honors hang high♪

415
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:56,060
♪The clouds dance in the air♪

416
00:18:56,060 --> 00:18:59,380
♪Brewing wine, we speak of legends♪

417
00:18:59,380 --> 00:19:03,100
♪In fine liquor,
true feelings are revealed♪

418
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:06,620
♪Washing away
a lifetime of wear and tear♪

419
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:09,500
♪Only for you♪

420
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:13,100
♪On the street of golden honors,
the music rises♪

421
00:19:13,220 --> 00:19:15,980
♪The moon moves west
beyond the pavilion♪

422
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:18,660
♪Wine runs dry, yet the revelry lingers♪

423
00:19:18,660 --> 00:19:22,740
♪In silk, I seek a kindred soul♪

424
00:19:22,740 --> 00:19:26,060
♪The rain has ceased,
clouds begin to clear♪

425
00:19:26,100 --> 00:19:29,460
♪The fragrant silk billows
under the low-hung stars♪

426
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:35,980
♪I'd cut the clouds and morning glow
to drape over you♪

427
00:19:37,060 --> 00:19:41,180
♪A single bolt of silk becomes♪

428
00:19:42,460 --> 00:19:46,980
♪Your wedding gown♪
